<div class="container">
  <div class="header-container">
    <h1>Top Movies API</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="description">
    <p>A simple API that returns basic information about the top 250 movies listed in IMDb. Data is scraped from <%= link_to "IMDb", "https://www.imdb.com/chart/top" %>.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="usage-container">
    <h2>Usage:</h2>
    <div class="usage">
      <h3>Retrieve all movies</h3>
      <p>Request URL: <em>https://top-250-movies-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/movies</em></p>
    </div>
    <div class="usage">
      <h3>Retrieve a specific movie</h3>
      <p>Request URL: <em>https://top-250-movies-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/movies/#ID</em></p>
      <p>Sample Usage: <em>https://top-250-movies-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/movies/1</em></p>
    </div>
    <div class="usage">
      <h3>Retrieve a movie or movies using keywords(Movie title, Director, Actor's name, Year of release and Genre)</h3>
      <p>Request URL: <em>https://top-250-movies-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/search?query=#KEYWORD</em></p>
      <p>Sample Usages: <br>
        <em>https://top-250-movies-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/search?query=inception</em></p>
      <p><em>https://top-250-movies-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/search?query=nolan</em></p>
      <p><em>https://top-250-movies-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/search?query=bale</em></p>
      <p><em>https://top-250-movies-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/search?query=2009</em></p>
      <p><em>https://top-250-movies-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/search?query=drama</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-row align-items-center">
    <div class="col-sm-10 my-1">
      <label class="sr-only" for="inlineFormInputName">URL</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="api-query" placeholder="Type the URL here">
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-2 my-1">
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100" id="api-button">Search</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border w-100 h-50" id="api-display"></div>
</div>